        <item>
            <title>NETA X 純電 SUV 香港發佈，主動安全系統齊備 + 續航里程 480 公里</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/05/25/neta-x/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=neta-x</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/05/25/neta-x/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 25 May 2024 05:41:48 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[汽車科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[NETA]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[NETA AYA]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[NETA GT]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[NETA S]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[NETA X]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1237942</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>大昌行汽車旗下首間「NETA Hong Kong 全新旗艦陳列室」正式於九龍灣開幕，NETA Hong Kong 同步發布最新旗艦級電動 SUV &#8211; NETA X，同場亦展出包括 N<wbr />ETA AYA、NETA S 和科技純電跑車 NETA GT 共四款型號，而 NETA 售<wbr />後服務中心亦於即日起為車主投入服務。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1237950 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240524_150214-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240524_150214-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240524_150214-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲NETA X 續航里程為 480 公里</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">NETA X 採用了最大功率 163 匹馬力的前置單摩打，與之搭載的是磷酸鐵鋰電池組，純電續航里程為 480 公里（NEDC），30 分鐘可由 30% 充電至 80%。車身⻑闊高分別為 4,619mm*1,860mm*1,628mm，擁有 2,770mm 的軸距，80% 的車內空間以頂級柔軟材質所覆蓋。此外，還配備 15.6 吋輕觸式顯示熒幕和 Apple CarPlay 連接。NETA X 還提供了 Intelligent 版本，包含 12 款 NETA 高精度感測主動式安全系統（包括塞車輔助、道路偏離預警、盲點偵察等功能）、全景天幕連電動太陽簾、360° 泊車鏡頭、電動尾門、駕駛席座椅記憶及迎賓功能等配置。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">NETA X 車頭採用了封閉式鬼面罩設計，強化了車身的空氣動力學表現。格柵兩側鋭利的頭燈組合採用分離式設計，上部為 LED 日間行車燈，下部為一體式的頭燈設計。配上前包圍兩側的通風口，整個車頭的設計有力量感。NETA X 側面線條流暢，Fastback 水滴形側背流線車身，尾部貫穿式 LED 尾燈設計，提升了整體的運動感。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1237952 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240524_150710-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240524_150710-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240524_150710-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1237977 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240524_150831-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240524_150831-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240524_150831-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲NETA X 車頭採用了封閉式鬼面罩設計，強化了車身的空氣動力學表現</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">NETA X 以「都市天際線」作為內裝設計主題，採用簡潔且具科技感的設計風格，配合環抱式設計。特大尾箱空間為 508 公升，後排座椅摺疊後可擴展至 1,388 公升。車內的 15.6 吋高清輕觸式顯示熒幕整合了車內大部份控制功能。NETA X 搭載了最新的「NETA L2 等級智能駕駛輔助系統」，協助駕駛者輕鬆處理路面狀況。 此外，車載系統還支援智慧語音助手，使用者只需透過簡單的英文語音指令就能完成大部分功能的控制。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1237960 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240524_150756-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240524_150756-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240524_150756-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1237961 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240524_150956-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240524_150956-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240524_150956-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>▲NETA X 以「都市天際線」作為內裝設計主題，採用簡潔且具科技感的設計風格</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1237954 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240524_150739-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240524_150739-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240524_150739-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1237962 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240524_150813-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240524_150813-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240524_150813-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲特大尾箱空間為 508 公升，後排座椅摺疊後可擴展至 1,388 公升</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1237956 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240524_150915-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240524_150915-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240524_150915-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲車內的 15.6 吋高清輕觸式顯示熒幕整合了車內大部份控制功能</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1237963 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240524_150913-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240524_150913-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240524_150913-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲NETA X 搭載了最新的「NETA L2 等級智能駕駛輔助系統」</p><div class="page" title="Page 2"><div class="layoutArea"><div class="column"><p>NETA X 將提供極智黑、珍珠白、魅影灰、冰川藍、琥珀棕五款車身顏色。NETA X 一換一税制下登場價為 HK$229,800。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1237965 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240524_150607-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240524_150607-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240524_150607-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p></div></div></div><p style="font-weight: 400; text-align: center;">▲NETA X 一換一税制下登場價為 HK$229,800</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">同場加映的 NETA 全新 SUV 車型 NETA AYA 正式登陸香港。車身顏色上，NETA AYA 共提供五款潮流配色：榛子米、晴空藍、霧面白、湖泊綠和魅影灰。NETA AYA 一換一税制下新售價為 HK$160,377。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1237969 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/neta_aya-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/neta_aya-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/neta_aya-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲NETA AYA 一換一税制下新售價為 HK$160,377</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">NETA S 作為運動型智能房車，配備業界領先級硬件、豪華舒適配置及領先的智能化水平，採用「科技融合極動」設計美學，使用一對歐翼式前門。NETA S 體現了空氣動力學性能與美學設計的融合。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1237970 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/neta_s_01-694x439.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="439" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/neta_s_01-694x439.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/neta_s_01.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲NETA S 採用「科技融合極動」設計美學，使用一對歐翼式前門</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">NETA GT 採用了雙門四座佈局，側身曲線流暢自然，既兼顧了空氣動力學，又為用户帶來更穩定、更動感的視覺感受。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1237975 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/neta_gt-694x430.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="430" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/neta_gt-694x430.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/neta_gt-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="font-weight: 400; text-align: center;">▲NETA GT 採用了雙門四座佈局，側身曲線流暢自然</p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/25/neta-x/life-tech/auto/">NETA X 純電 SUV 香港發佈，主動安全系統齊備 + 續航里程 480 公里</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
